name: Dinosaur'us
overview: Dinosaur'us leads you into a forgotten world where Dinosaurs were Kings! Take control of these incredible creatures on your Gameboy Color.Nurture your Dinosaur from a hatchling to fully grown to survive the numerous dangers in their predatory habitats. Look for food, defeat other dinosaurs to obtain new power ups and evolve your species. For the ultimate challenge fight with your friends' Dinosaurs using the Gameboy link cable. It is a cruel world in which only the smartest and the biggest will survive!
